headline: VETS Indexes Names Teradyne 2025 Recognized Employer
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., May 13, 2025--Teradyne, (NASDAQ:TER), a leading supplier of automated test solutions, was awarded by VETS Indexes as a Recognized Employer in the 2025 VETS Indexes Employer Awards. Teradyne has now achieved this recognition for three straight years, dating back to 2023.
